## Indicators of Compromise (IOCs)

### Domains

```text
gruta.com.mx
server.cubatiendaalimentos.com.mx
```

### Software / Process Names

```text
SimpleHelp
ScreenConnect
elev_win.exe
```

### Behavioral Indicators

```text
Windows service creation
Safe Mode persistence
SeDebugPrivilege acquisition
AdjustTokenPrivileges usage
WMI queries to root\SecurityCenter2
Security product enumeration every 67 seconds
User presence polling every 23 seconds
Remote desktop interaction
```

---

## KQL Detection Rule (Microsoft Sentinel)

```kql
DeviceNetworkEvents
| where Timestamp > ago(30d)
| where RemoteUrl has_any (
    "gruta.com.mx",
    "server.cubatiendaalimentos.com.mx"
)
or InitiatingProcessFileName in~ (
    "SimpleHelp.exe",
    "ScreenConnect.ClientService.exe",
    "elev_win.exe"
)
| project Timestamp,
          DeviceName,
          RemoteUrl,
          InitiatingProcessFileName,
          InitiatingProcessCommandLine,
          InitiatingProcessAccountName
| order by Timestamp desc
```

## Hunting Recommendations

- Revisar instalaciones recientes de **SimpleHelp** y **ScreenConnect**
- Validar creación sospechosa de servicios en endpoints
- Monitorear procesos que soliciten **SeDebugPrivilege**
- Detectar conexiones salientes hacia dominios `.mx` no habituales
- Correlacionar eventos de acceso remoto con correos de phishing recientes

## Severity

**High**

## Threat Type

**Phishing → Initial Access → Persistence → Remote Access → Potential Ransomware Deployment**
